{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would have to attend-- otherwise I wouldn't be attending school in this country because I was, you know, formally finished with school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- it was felt-- and I think I felt that, too-- that it would be of advantage to, to go to school, to go to high school in this country.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so my father and I went to Liverpool and boarded a Cunard liner there called the S-A-M-A-R-I-A.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think she was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1940, summer of 1940, May of 1940, probably.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first we went to, to London and saw the sights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a cousin there, who had gotten out earlier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and, and then we went to Liverpool.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In London, I guess we had to see the American consulate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to go to Liverpool, which was fairly close to, to Manchester, and took the, the boat from there and zigzagged across the Atlantic, because there were U-boats in the Atlantic.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was their way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was 10 days on the Atlantic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was seasick again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I, I don't like ocean liners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And got here, and some cousins of my father's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] welcomed us into this country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, what day and year was this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in May, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know the exact date anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we stayed at, at this cousin's for a little while.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father then took a room in a, in a, in an apartment, which was sort of a boarding house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he got his meals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and he had a, a room to himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got to stay with the son of a cousin of his.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In other words, he was a second cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
